Name: Puli Inu
Description: Pulimatic will be an app that combines multiple crypto features like a crypto wallet, a Dex that can be used to swap to your favorite tokens, play to earn games, and chat & discussion room. Pulimatic also plans to own a Gaming LaunchPad. Puli Inu has a total supply of 100,000,000. According to the white paper, 4% of the total supply and 6% were distributed to Liquidity and marketing respectively. There’s no information about the tax structure.  Telegram | Instagram
